body:
You can use the [$addFields](manual/reference/operator/aggregation/addFields) stage to add new fields
with calculated values using [aggregation operators](manual/reference/mql/expressions).

> **Note:** `$addFields` is similar to [$project](manual/reference/operator/aggregation/project) but does not allow you to
> include or omit fields.

> **Example:** The following `$addFields` stages creates a new field named
> `numItems` where the value is the number of documents in the
> `items` array:
>
> ```javascript
> {
>   "$addFields": {
>     "numItems": { "$sum": { "$size": "$items" } }
>   }
> }
> ```
